{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"body":"Ninth remediation: defined the focused finder prompt file, system judgment rules, delimited subject/prerequisite input format, exact coverage and finding output obligations, and deterministic ownership of indeterminate results. Also specified focused-verifier context recovery and added named largest-window and observability tests with exact assertions."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784568398862730001,"uuid":"b89255e2-762d-406d-86d6-5580de278113"}